\fBtorf\fP \fB\-i\fP \fIINPUT\fP [\fIOPTIONS\fP] \fB\-o\fP \fITORRENT\fP
.br
Edit the existing torrent file or magnet URI \fIINPUT\fP (e.g. to fix a typo) and
create the new torrent file \fITORRENT\fP.
