       \-t http://example.org:6881/announce \(rs
       \-t http://example.com:6881/announce \(rs
       \-\-nodate
.fi
.if n .RE
.sp
Read \(lqfoo.torrent\(rq and print its metainfo:
.sp
.if n .RS 4
.nf
$ torf \-i foo.torrent
.fi
.if n .RE
